	<element name="Ancient Whip of Monster Slaying" type="Magic Item" source=">:P" id="ID_CMF_WHIP_OF_MONSTER_SLAYING">
		<description>
			<p>This extra long chain whip with a finely crafted silver tip is assembled into interlocking sections allowing the hunter to adjust it according to his prey.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Adjustable</em></strong> During a short or long rest, the hunter may adjust the length of this whip by connecting or disconnecting sections of the chain.</p>
			<p class="indent"><strong><em>Whipcrack</em></strong> Gain an additional die of weapon damage if the prey is at the specified distance away from the hunter and no other creature is between them.</p>
			<table>
				<thead>
					<tr><td>Whip Length</td><td>Weapon Range</td><td>Whipcrack Distance</td></tr>
				</thead>
				<tr><td>Short</td><td>5</td><td>5</td></tr>
				<tr><td>Medium</td><td>5-10</td><td>10</td></tr>
				<tr><td>Long</td><td>10-15</td><td>15</td></tr>
			</table>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Magic Weapons</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">0</set>
			<set name="type" addition="whip">Weapon</set>
			<set name="rarity">Artifact</set>
			<set name="weapon">Whip</set>
			<set name="enhancement">0</set>
			<set name="attunement">true</set>
			<set name="name-format">{{parent}} +{{enhancement}}</set>
			<set name="slot">onehand</set>
			<set name="damage" type="slashing">1d4</set>
			<set name="proficiency">ID_PROFICIENCY_WEAPON_PROFICIENCY_WHIP</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
